    <Heading Size="HeadingSize.Is5">Controller Setup</Heading>

    <ListGroup>
        <ListGroupItem>
            1. Register or unregister the COM controller with <Code>FFlips Controller Register.exe</Code>. 
            This controller handles communicating with the server from inside a pinball simulator.
        </ListGroupItem>
        <ListGroupItem>
            2. Copy the <Code>FlippingFlipsScore.vbs</Code> script file to the global scripts directory.
            This file contains functions that the table can use and initializes the Flips.Controller.
        </ListGroupItem>
        <ListGroupItem>
            3. Download a settings file for your machine in your <Blazorise.Link To="/mymachine">MyMachine</Blazorise.Link> page and place it where you launch the table from.
            This file has settings that holds the <Code>SeverUrl</Code> and <Code>ApiKey</Code>
        </ListGroupItem>
    </ListGroup>
